snippet: SooBin Kim shot a course-record nine-under 63 to leave Lydia Ko, the defending champion and top-ranked women’s player, seven strokes behind in the Women’s Australian Open in Adelaide.
abstract: SooBin Kim takes lead at Women's Australian Open, shooting course-record nine-under 63.
lead_paragraph: SooBin Kim shot a course-record nine-under 63 to leave Lydia Ko, the defending champion and top-ranked women’s player, seven strokes behind in the Women’s Australian Open in Adelaide.

headline.main: SooBin Kim Grabs Lead in Women’s Australian Open
